               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200412-38-cd207" type="crimeDate">22d of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200412-38-off206 t18200412-38-cd207"></join>, in the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200412-38-victim385" type="victimName">
                           Charles 
                           Hepburn
                        <interp inst="t18200412-38-victim385" type="surname" value="Hepburn"></interp>
